sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS pod-to-pod
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>TLS pod-to-pod
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>8001/TCP HTTP<br/>TLS pod-to-pod
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PipelinePod as Pipeline Pod<br/>Executor
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS pod-to-pod
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via Dashboard

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token
    OAuth->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Store pipeline metadata<br/>DB Password + TLS
    API->>WFC: HTTP/8001<br/>Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>K8s: HTTPS/6443<br/>Create Workflow<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>API: Pipeline Created
    API-->>User: 200 OK

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    WFC->>K8s: HTTPS/6443<br/>Create Pipeline Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>PipelinePod: Pod Started
    PipelinePod->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Get pipeline params<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>PipelinePod: Pipeline config
    PipelinePod->>S3: HTTPS/443<br/>Download input artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials (IAM/Access Key)
    S3-->>PipelinePod: Artifacts
    PipelinePod->>PipelinePod: Execute task
    PipelinePod->>MLMD: gRPC/8080<br/>Record artifact lineage<br/>mTLS
    MLMD->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Store metadata<br/>DB Password + TLS
    PipelinePod->>S3: HTTPS/443<br/>Upload output artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials
    PipelinePod->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Report task completion<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    PA->>API: gRPC/8887<br/>Query workflow status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    PA->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Sync workflow state<br/>DB Password + TLS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Lineage Tracking

    PipelinePod->>MLMD: gRPC/8080<br/>Log execution context<br/>mTLS
    MLMD->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Store artifact relationships<br/>DB Password + TLS
    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/{id}<br/>OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS (Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Query artifact lineage<br/>DB Password + TLS
    MariaDB-->>API: Lineage data
    API-->>User: Artifact graph

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    activate WFC
    WFC->>WFC: Cron trigger activated
    WFC->>API: gRPC/8887<br/>Create pipeline run<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API->>MariaDB: MySQL/3306<br/>Store run metadata<br/>DB Password + TLS
    API->>WFC: HTTP/8001<br/>Submit workflow<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>K8s: HTTPS/6443<br/>Create workflow pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    deactivate WFC
